{
  "texts": [
    "OpenAI is a research laboratory founded in 2015 (Brockman et al., 2016).",
    "This laboratory has achieved results in the development of AI technologies and has released several machine learning products to the public, including DALL-E and ChatGPT (Devlin et al., 2018).",
    "DALL-E can generate images using artificial neural networks (Cherian et al., 2022).",
    "ChatGPT, as well as other models such as Google BERT (Bidirectional Encoder Representations from Transformers) and leading language models developed by Microsoft (XLNet) are all based on the GPT-3 architecture.",
    "BERT and XLNet, on the other hand, focus primarily on understanding the underlying meaning of the text."
  ]
}